OL,3,C'Much-loved' White Rhino dies at
OL,4,Csafari park
OL,6,FA much-loved White Rhino has died at
OL,7,FKnowsley Safari Park.
OL,9,FPiglet, who was around 40-years-old,
OL,10,Fhad been at the park, in Merseyside,
OL,11,Ffor 31 years.
OL,13,FShe had been experiencing "age-related
OL,14,Fhealth issues and had been monitored
OL,15,Fby keepers and vets for the last few
OL,16,Fweeks", the park said in a social
OL,17,Fmedia post, and died on 4 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
