OL,3,C'Much-loved' White Rhino dies at
OL,4,Csafari park
OL,6,F"She had a peaceful end to a long and
OL,7,Fhappy life at the Safari, and she will
OL,8,Fbe sorely missed by her keepers,
OL,9,Fguests and the rest of her crash," it
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FThe park has one of the largest white
OL,13,Frhino crashes in the UK, with the
OL,14,Fattraction's successful breeding
OL,15,Fprogramme helping to protect the rare
OL,16,Fand vulnerable species.
OL,18,FKamari was born in November 2025, to
OL,19,Fmum Bayami, who also gave birth to
OL,20,FBindi in February 2024.
